main event: During the night of 25/26 August 1956, radiant flying disks were sighted over the port of Tangier.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately ten seconds before the objects disappeared., Numerous persons witnessed the phenomenon., Observers described the objects as radiant flying disks., Weather conditions at the time of the sighting remain unknown., The report concluded various possibilities for the nature of the objects including aircraft, balloon, and astronomical.
